.nav__link:hover:after{transform:scale(1)}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.footer__nav{grid-column:2/-2;gap:120px}}@media screen and (min-width:1280px){.footer__nav{gap:85px;grid-column:7/-1;margin-top:0;padding-top:0;padding-left:65px;border-top:none;border-left:1px solid rgba(26,90,76,.5)}}
